色都全部采用手工。动画角色的动作无懈可击，可以说达到了2D动画的极限；极富艺术感的各种设计与效果让人眼花缭乱。而最令人赞叹的无过于影片中完美的3D效果，3D感一直也是影片的制作理念，和其他手绘动画不同的是，该片镜头的移动会带动背景的透视变化！而且这些完全能够媲美电脑制作3D效果依然是手绘！可以说，Williams他们完成的部分堪称手绘动画历史上的最强音！而这也是这部动画在Richard Williams手中制作缓慢的一大原因。","name":"The Princess and the Cobbler","name_cn":"小偷与鞋匠","tags":[{"name":"欧美","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1995","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画电影","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Richard_Williams","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"神作","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"未完成作品","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"90年代","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧洲","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"英国","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"作画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"非日本动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"放松","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"理查德威廉姆斯","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"电影","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"小偷与鞋匠"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"阿拉伯骑士"},{"v":"The Thief and the Cobbler"},{"v":"Arabian Knight"},{"v":"两个阿拉伯骑士"}]},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1995-08-25"},{"key":"片长","value":"72 分钟 / 91 分钟(working print) / Australia: 77 分钟"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":28,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":1,"7":6,"8":8,"9":6,"10":6},"score":8.3},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":11,"dropped":3,"wish":105,"collect":34,"doing":10},"id":113264,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["剧场版","欧美"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1995-08-23","platform":"OVA","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/ea/28/37459_533Xx.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/ea/28/37459_533Xx.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/ea/28/37459_533Xx.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/ea/28/37459_533Xx.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/ea/28/37459_533Xx.jpg"},"summary":"以TOMY推出的玩具”バト